{"tid":891970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★仲有？】深水埗色情光碟中心　拘61歲男子","createTime":"2018-11-06T13:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T17:26:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"34ad5df51e0325a02821b68c043b32c9d8ac532d","tid":891970,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181106/photo/bkn-20181106192703205-1106_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181106211230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181106192703205-1106_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181106211230&h=77e072f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方近日接獲線報，指疑有黑幫於深水埗區售賣色情光碟，深水埗警區特別職務隊經深入調查後，今(6日)下午約1時，在區內展開反淫褻物品行動，突擊搜查鴨寮街一店舖，檢獲約<span style=\"color: red;\">9000隻色情光碟，總值約27萬元</span>。行動中拘捕一名姓劉(61歲)本地男子，他涉嫌「發布淫褻物品」及「管有淫褻物品以供發布用途」，現正被扣留調查。警方表示，相信今次行動已打擊三合會的收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181106/bkn-20181106192703205-1106_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181106%2Fbkn-20181106192703205-1106_00822_001.html&d=xly6xkOdUO7KnkCtzsZR7gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=85b892f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181106/bkn-20181106192703205-1106_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"452605a326ba1cb635421ab77a921b210e3fa67e","tid":891970,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12043881d39e4e2a5925ebd37206467b79fc5522","tid":891970,"uid":3241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"又拉夕陽工業...."},{"pid":"26bce07a993c6fc05859b842e6c74f9575c0dadc","tid":891970,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"啲廢老唔識bt係咁上下"},{"pid":"9c013de5036ee63594b61636e3141e160434e3fe","